We have to important thing in ansible-

1) Adhoc commands>running command in ansible way > running single command
      hostname
      ansible -i[inverntory] /etc/ansible/hosts -m[module] command -a[argument] "hostname" all[server group]


2) Playbook> collection of commands written in a particular formate > colection of commands
      ansible-playbook -i[inverntory] /etc/ansible/hosts nginx_install.yml[yaml location that container configuration]

Ansible configuration
=====================
Most of the configurations are by root, so unix team will do that, we should know how to use the tool.


